@startuml
'title US30 – System Sequence Diagram – Schedule Vaccine Administration

autoactivate on
autonumber

actor "SNS User" as SNSUser
participant ":System" as System

activate SNSUser

SNSUser -> System: asks to schedule a vaccine administration
System --> SNSUser: requests the vaccine type

SNSUser -> System: selects the intended vaccine type
System --> SNSUser: shows available vaccination centers \n and asks to select one

SNSUser -> System: selects the intended vaccination center
System --> SNSUser: shows available time slots \n and asks to select one

SNSUser -> System: selects the intended date/time slot \n and provides contact details
System --> SNSUser: shows an appointment preview \n and requests confirmation

SNSUser -> System: confirms the scheduling

alt appointment successfully created
  System --> SNSUser: informs operation success \n (appointment data and identifier)
else slot unavailable / validation error / existing future appointment
  System --> SNSUser: informs operation failure
end

@enduml
